  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"Vandozer\" is a punishing Trials-meets-QWOP vehicle romp, where mastering the unique controls is both the challenge and the reward.  </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.poster.avif?t=1594143386\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.webm?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.mp4?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Van Gameplay: </strong><br>While piloting Vandozer, use the van's three pistons in order to jump, climb, cling and grind your way through the challenging levels. The controls are completely physics-driven, so get creative with how you use the pistons. Unlock new regions on the world map and see if you can make it to \"The Final Climb\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.poster.avif?t=1594143386\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.webm?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.mp4?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Walker Gameplay: </strong><br>Tired of living in a van? Step into the giant G.O.A.T. Walker and manipulate each of the four legs independently. Make sure to lean left and right to ensure a balanced ride. Don’t worry if you lose a leg or two, the G.O.A.T. Walker is designed to persevere.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>\"Vandozer\" is a punishing Trials-meets-QWOP vehicle romp, where mastering the unique controls is both the challenge and the reward.  </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.poster.avif?t=1594143386\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.webm?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/d600d69d0938c4b1de4a7546938ef042.mp4?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Van Gameplay: </strong><br>While piloting Vandozer, use the van's three pistons in order to jump, climb, cling and grind your way through the challenging levels. The controls are completely physics-driven, so get creative with how you use the pistons. Unlock new regions on the world map and see if you can make it to \"The Final Climb\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.poster.avif?t=1594143386\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.webm?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/802260/extras/f95817522d63d2930cf50668ea2dfa73.mp4?t=1594143386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Walker Gameplay: </strong><br>Tired of living in a van? Step into the giant G.O.A.T. Walker and manipulate each of the four legs independently. Make sure to lean left and right to ensure a balanced ride. Don’t worry if you lose a leg or two, the G.O.A.T. Walker is designed to persevere.",
